            "notes": "This deck focuses on utilizing the powerful commander, Rafiq of the Many, to create a fast and aggressive strategy. The deck includes a mix of versatile creatures and powerful equipment to quickly build a threatening board presence. Cards like Swords to Plowshares, Counterspell, and Force of Will provide disruption and protection, while mana dorks like Noble Hierarch and Birds of Paradise help to ramp up quickly. The deck also includes a variety of land destruction spells like Armageddon and Wasteland to disrupt opponents' mana bases. Overall, the key concept of this deck is to apply consistent pressure on the opponent, utilizing Rafiq's ability to pump up creatures and deal massive damage efficiently."
