            "notes": "This deck focuses on reanimation and graveyard manipulation to assemble powerful creature combos. It utilizes counterspells and disruption to protect its game plan while also having access to strong card draw and tutoring effects to find its key pieces. The Mimeoplasm serves as both a reanimation target and a potential win condition by copying powerful creatures from the graveyard. The deck includes a variety of combo pieces and utility creatures to facilitate different game plans depending on the matchup. It also features a strong mana base with a mix of dual lands and fetch lands to ensure consistent mana production. Overall, the deck aims to out-value and out-maneuver opponents through efficient creature reanimation and resource manipulation."
